sns.set(style="whitegrid")
plt.figure(figsize=(8,5))
total = float(len(Toy_story_rating))
ax = sns.countplot(x="Rating", hue="Age", data=Toy_story_rating)
plt.title('Toy story rating', fontsize=20)
for p in ax.patches:
    percentage = '{:.1f}%'.format(100 * p.get_height()/total)
    x = p.get_x() + p.get_width()
    y = p.get_height()
    ax.annotate(percentage, (x, y))
plt.show()
